contents:
[package]
name = "mpris2-zbus"
description = "zbus-based bindings for MPRIS2 (Media Player Remote Interfacing Specification) on Linux"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"
license = "MPL-2.0"

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0"
zbus = "3.7"
zvariant = "3.10"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.time]
version = "0.3"
features = [ "parsing",]

[dev-dependencies.miette]
version = "4.3"
features = [ "fancy",]

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = [ "full",]

[[bench]]
name = "stress_test"
harness = false

[[example]]
name = "simple"
path = "examples/simple.rs"
doc-scrape-examples = true

[package]
name = "relm4"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/relm4/"
version = "0.7.0-beta.2"
authors = [ "Aaron Erhardt <aaron.erhardt@t-online.de>",]
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.65"
readme = "README.md"
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
description = "An idiomatic GUI library inspired by Elm and based on gtk4-rs"
homepage = "https://relm4.org"
repository = "https://github.com/Relm4/Relm4"
keywords = [ "gui", "gtk", "gtk4", "elm",]
categories = [ "gui",]

[features]
default = [ "macros", "gnome_42",]
libadwaita = [ "adw",]
macros = [ "relm4-macros",]
gnome_45 = [ "gnome_44", "gtk/gnome_45", "adw/v1_4",]
gnome_44 = [ "gnome_43", "gtk/gnome_44", "adw/v1_3",]
gnome_43 = [ "gnome_42", "gtk/gnome_43", "adw/v1_2",]
gnome_42 = [ "gtk/gnome_42",]
all = [ "macros", "libadwaita",]

[dependencies]
flume = "0.11.0"
futures = "0.3.28"
fragile = "2.0.0"
once_cell = "1.18"
tracing = "0.1.37"
async-trait = "0.1.68"

[dev-dependencies]
rand = "0.8.5"
tracker = "0.2"
reqwest = "0.11.18"
tracing-subscriber = "0.3.17"
serde_json = "1"

[dependencies.adw]
version = "0.5"
optional = true
package = "libadwaita"

[dependencies.gtk]
version = "0.7"
package = "gtk4"

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.28"
features = [ "rt", "rt-multi-thread", "sync",]

[dependencies.relm4-macros]
version = "0.7.0-alpha.1"
path = "../relm4-macros"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.relm4-macros]
path = "../relm4-macros"

[dev-dependencies.criterion]
version = "0.5"
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.relm4-icons]
git = "https://github.com/Relm4/icons"
features = [ "plus", "minus", "tag-outline-add", "delete-filled",]

[dev-dependencies.relm4-components]
path = "../relm4-components"

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.28"
features = [ "rt", "macros", "time", "rt-multi-thread",]

[dev-dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive", "default",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true
rustc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
cargo-args = [ "-Zunstable-options", "-Zrustdoc-scrape-examples",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[[example]]
name = "web_image"
required-features = [ "web",]

[[example]]
name = "adw_combo_row"
required-features = [ "libadwaita",]

[package]
name = "relm4-components"
readme = "README.md"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/relm4_components/"
version = "0.7.0-beta.2"
authors = [ "Aaron Erhardt <aaron.erhardt@t-online.de>",]
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.65"
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
description = "An idiomatic GUI library inspired by Elm and based on gtk4-rs"
homepage = "https://relm4.org"
repository = "https://github.com/Relm4/Relm4"
keywords = [ "gui", "gtk", "gtk4", "elm",]
categories = [ "gui",]

[dependencies]
once_cell = "1.18"
tracker = "0.2.1"

[features]
default = [ "libadwaita",]
dox = [ "web",]
web = [ "reqwest",]
libadwaita = [ "relm4/libadwaita",]

[dependencies.relm4]
version = "0.7.0-alpha.1"
path = "../relm4"
default-features = false
features = [ "macros",]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11.18"
optional = true

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true
rustc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
cargo-args = [ "-Zunstable-options", "-Zrustdoc-scrape-examples",]

[package]
name = "relm4-macros"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "gui", "gtk", "gtk4", "elm", "view",]
documentation = "https://docs.rs/relm4_macros/"
version = "0.7.0-beta.2"
authors = [ "Aaron Erhardt <aaron.erhardt@t-online.de>",]
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.65"
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
description = "An idiomatic GUI library inspired by Elm and based on gtk4-rs"
homepage = "https://relm4.org"
repository = "https://github.com/Relm4/Relm4"
categories = [ "gui",]

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[features]
default = [ "relm4",]
relm4 = []

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "1.0"
quote = "1.0"

[dev-dependencies]
rustversion = "1"
trybuild = "1.0.80"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "2.0"
features = [ "full", "extra-traits", "visit", "visit-mut",]

[dev-dependencies.relm4]
path = "../relm4"

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/pop-os/mpris2-zbus"]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/mpris2-zbus"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/relm4/relm4"]
git = "https://github.com/relm4/relm4"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
